net.siot.android.gateway

Class SiotNetGatewayManagerMobile

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.siot.android.gateway.SiotNetGatewayManagerMobile

  • public class SiotNetGatewayManagerMobile
extends java.lang.Object
    siot.net gateway library SiotNetGatewayManagerMobile. Use to connect the mobile device and a wearable to the siot.net and using the sensorservice correctly configured. Created by Sathesh Paramasamy on 28.10.15.
